    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚实施道路封锁后科索沃关闭两处边境口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/kosovo-closes-two-border-sites-following-serbian-road-blockades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，塞尔维亚团体拦截了部分持有科索沃证件的旅客，随后科索沃关闭了与塞尔维亚的两个边境口岸，导致该地区的紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/kosovo-closes-two-border-sites-following-serbian-road-blockades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 09:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国新总理将推进现金刺激计划以振兴经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/new-thai-pm-to-push-ahead-with-cash-stimulus-to-revive-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任总理巴东丹·西那瓦誓言要推进备受争议的 140 亿美元现金刺激计划，其内阁已敲定蓝图，旨在帮助东南亚第二大经济体摆脱长期低增长和家庭债务困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/new-thai-pm-to-push-ahead-with-cash-stimulus-to-revive-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 05:45:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度执政党在选举前承诺为脆弱地区提供就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/india-ruling-party-pledges-jobs-in-fragile-region-ahead-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度执政党承诺在本月晚些时候举行的地方选举之前，在动荡的查谟和克什米尔地区创造 50 万个就业岗位，并安置克什米尔潘迪特人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/india-ruling-party-pledges-jobs-in-fragile-region-ahead-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 05:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党大获全胜的老将纷纷跨越大西洋前来援助哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/veterans-of-labour-s-big-win-flock-across-atlantic-to-aid-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默在其政党近二十年来首次赢得选举胜利几天后就登上了飞往华盛顿的飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/veterans-of-labour-s-big-win-flock-across-atlantic-to-aid-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲为争夺天然气而展开战争，为阿尔及利亚选举助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/europe-s-war-driven-hunt-for-gas-hands-algeria-an-election-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五年前的选举让阿尔及利亚陷入抗议浪潮和经济危机，而欧洲对能源的追逐则导致该国命运发生急剧逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/europe-s-war-driven-hunt-for-gas-hands-algeria-an-election-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾法院允许前市长参加参议院调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/philippine-court-allows-ex-mayor-to-attend-senate-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，菲律宾法院允许被解职的市长郭文婧参加周一举行的参议院听证会，该听证会涉及与以中国为中心的在线赌场有关的非法活动。几天前，郭文婧在印度尼西亚被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/philippine-court-allows-ex-mayor-to-attend-senate-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 00:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉因骚扰指控解雇人权部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/lula-fires-human-rights-minister-over-harassment-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将人权部长一事解雇，因为性骚扰指控令这位总统感到尴尬，而维护妇女权利是总统工作的重中之重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/lula-fires-human-rights-minister-over-harassment-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 22:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥反对派称已获得投票阻止 AMLO 改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/mexican-opposition-says-it-has-votes-to-block-amlo-s-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥反对派誓言阻止总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔对参议院司法系统提出的备受争议的改革，目前执政联盟距离获得修改宪法所需的三分之二多数票仅一步之遥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/mexican-opposition-says-it-has-votes-to-block-amlo-s-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 19:17:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗无视美国和欧盟的警告，向俄罗斯发射弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/iran-sends-russia-ballistic-missiles-despite-us-eu-warnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，尽管美国和欧洲官员数月来警告伊朗不要这样做，但伊朗仍向俄罗斯运送弹道导弹，以协助其在乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/iran-sends-russia-ballistic-missiles-despite-us-eu-warnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
